## QUICK REFERENCE: TABLE NAMES
- `users` — auth + telegram binding
- `raw_entries` — append-only capture log (NEVER delete from this)
- `articles` — synthesised wiki content
- `document_chunks` — vector embeddings (768-dim, HNSW index)
- `backlinks` — graph edges (wikilinks + accepted tunnels)
- `tunnel_suggestions` — pending/accepted/rejected AI-found connections
- `dislike_pairs` — permanent rejection log
- `diff_suggestions` — differential synthesis outputs
- `nudges` — edit suggestions
- `media_files` — file storage index
- `llm_usage` — LLM cost/performance log

